data.text:
What's special

Lots of windowsIn-home washers and dryers

Cascade Summit offers one, two and three-bedroom flats and townhomes with individual addresses in West Linn. Our spacious floor plans boasts lots of windows to provide ample amounts of sunlight, private balconies / patios with views and in-home washers and dryers. We are near Lake Oswego and are located in the West Linn-Wilsonville School District. Cascade Summit is zoned to Trillium Creek Elementary School, Rosemont Ridge Middle School and West Linn High School.
